# 🌞 Summer Training Project

## 📌 Overview
This repository contains the work completed during my **45-Day Summer Training Internship (June – July 2025)**. Throughout the training, I gained practical knowledge by working on real-world programming tasks, web development projects, and problem-solving exercises.

---

## 🎯 Objectives
- Strengthen programming fundamentals
- Learn modern web development concepts
- Build real-world projects
- Improve logical and problem-solving skills
- Gain hands-on development experience

